<subSubSection id="C3466511FFCBFFF77581AA9BC480AD46" pageId="8" pageNumber="514" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BE3369AFFCBFFF77581AA9BC480AD46" blockId="8.[151,1437,150,285]" pageId="8" pageNumber="514">
<emphasis id="B928EA88FFCBFFF77581AA9BC756ACEB" bold="true" box="[199,315,150,176]" pageId="8" pageNumber="514">Remarks.</emphasis>
This species was originally described on the basis of a single female specimen from 
<collectingRegion id="4998F878FFCBFFF7718EAA9AC378ACEA" box="[1224,1301,151,177]" country="Bolivia" name="La Paz" pageId="8" pageNumber="514">La Paz</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingCountry id="F34B760AFFCBFFF77059AA9BC302ACEB" box="[1311,1391,150,176]" name="Bolivia" pageId="8" pageNumber="514">Bolivia</collectingCountry>
and presently it is in poor condition. It was associated with specimens from Quincemil, 
<collectingRegion id="4998F878FFCBFFF7715CAAB7C20FAC8F" box="[1050,1122,186,212]" country="Peru" name="Cusco" pageId="8" pageNumber="514">Cuzco</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingCountry id="F34B760AFFCBFFF7712AAAB6C2F3AC8E" box="[1132,1182,187,213]" name="Peru" pageId="8" pageNumber="514">Peru</collectingCountry>
by 
<bibRefCitation id="EFCD4B6BFFCBFFF77180AAB7C68EACA3" author="Rafael, J. A. &amp; Cumming, J. M." pageId="8" pageNumber="514" pagination="613 - 624" refId="ref17345" refString="Rafael, J. A. &amp; Cumming, J. M. (2010) Revision of the genus Macrostomus Wiedemann (Diptera: Empididae: Empidinae). II. The pictipennis species-group. Acta Amazonica, 40, 613 - 624. https: // doi. org / 10.1590 / S 0044 - 59672010000300023" type="journal article" year="2010">Rafael &amp; Cumming (2010)</bibRefCitation>
. No male from the type-locality was studied and this is essential to be secure that the Peruvian specimens are conspecific with Bolivian specimens of 
<taxonomicName id="4C5C4D19FFCBFFF7770DAB0EC48BAD47" authorityName="" baseAuthorityName="Bezzi" baseAuthorityYear="1909" box="[587,742,259,284]" class="Insecta" family="Empididae" genus="Macrostomus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="514" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="pictipennis">
<emphasis id="B928EA88FFCBFFF7770DAB0EC48BAD47" box="[587,742,259,284]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="514">M. pictipennis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
